  @{b}Welcome!@{ub}

  @{fg shine}@{" Tom's Magic WB Icons Number 3 " SYSTEM "TIGuide/Sound TIGuide/RockNRol.snd q"}@{fg text}                                                    26-Aug-95

  MagicWB2.0-Style Icons and other stuff in a 16 colour format.


  Don't worry if these icons look a little strange at first, I'm no @{" turkey " SYSTEM "TIGuide/Sound TIGuide/gobble.snd q"} it's just 
  that you haven't installed the correct @{" 16 colour palette. " LINK "16Col"} ;->


  Please read on on how to make your workbench compatible with the colour prefs used by many of 
  the world's greatest icon creators!


     @{" · " LINK "prefs"}   Preferences Icons
     @{" · " LINK "point"}   Colour & Pointer
